"phegguṃ atikkamma tacaṃ, papaṭikaṃ chetvā ādāya pakkameyya ‘sāran’ti "
"maññamāno."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was another person in need of heartwood … he’d cut off the "
"shoots and depart imagining they were heartwood …"

msgctxt "mn30:4.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ cakkhumā puriso disvā evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:4.3"
msgid ""
