"mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva sāraṃ, phegguṃ chetvā ādāya "
"pakkanto “sāran”ti maññamāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:6.5"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ nānubhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.200"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:7.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi vā pana, brāhmaṇa, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ "
"caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato sāraññeva chetvā ādāya "
"pakkameyya ‘sāran’ti jānamāno."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was another person in need of heartwood. And while wandering "
"in search of heartwood he’d come across a large tree standing with "
"heartwood. He’d cut out just the heartwood and depart knowing it was "
"heartwood."

msgctxt "mn30:7.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ cakkhumā puriso disvā evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "If a person with good eyesight saw him they’d say:"

msgctxt "mn30:7.3"
msgid ""
"‘aññāsi vatāyaṃ bhavaṃ puriso sāraṃ, aññāsi phegguṃ, aññāsi tacaṃ, aññāsi "
"papaṭikaṃ, aññāsi sākhāpalāsaṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘This gentleman knows what heartwood, softwood, bark, shoots, or branches "
"and leaves are."

msgctxt "mn30:7.4"
msgid ""
"Tathā hayaṃ bhavaṃ puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ caramāno "
"mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato sāraññeva chetvā ādāya pakkanto “sāran”ti "
"jānamāno."
msgstr ""
"That’s why he cut out just the heartwood and departed knowing it was "
"heartwood."

msgctxt "mn30:7.5"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ anubhavissatī’ti."
msgstr "Whatever he needs to make from heartwood, he will succeed.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:8.1"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco puggalo saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajito hoti:"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, take a certain person who goes forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness, thinking:"

msgctxt "mn30:8.2"
msgid ""
"‘otiṇṇomhi jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi "
"upāyāsehi, dukkhotiṇṇo dukkhapareto, "
msgstr ""
"‘I’m swamped by rebirth, old age, and death; by sorrow, lamentation, pain, "
"sadness, and distress. I’m swamped by suffering, mired in suffering. "

msgctxt "mn30:8.3"
msgid ""
"appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethā’ti."
msgstr "Hopefully I can find an end to this entire mass of suffering.’"

msgctxt "mn30:8.4"
msgid "So evaṃ pabbajito samāno lābhasakkārasilokaṃ abhinibbatteti."
msgstr ""
"When they’ve gone forth they generate possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "mn30:8.5"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena attamano hoti paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr "They’re happy with that, and they’ve got all they wished for."

msgctxt "mn30:8.6"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti:"
msgstr "And they glorify themselves and put others down on account of that:"

msgctxt "mn30:8.7"
msgid ""
"‘ahamasmi lābhasakkārasilokavā, ime panaññe bhikkhū appaññātā appesakkhā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I’m the one with possessions, honor, and popularity. These other mendicants "
"are obscure and insignificant.’"

msgctxt "mn30:8.8"
msgid ""
"Lābhasakkārasilokena ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ sacchikiriyāya na chandaṃ janeti, na vāyamati, olīnavuttiko ca "
"hoti sāthaliko."
msgstr ""
"They become lazy and slack regarding their possessions, honor, and "
"popularity, not generating enthusiasm or trying to realize those things that "
"are better and finer. …"

msgctxt "mn30:8.9"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi so, brāhmaṇa, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ "
"caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva sāraṃ atikkamma "
"phegguṃ atikkamma tacaṃ atikkamma papaṭikaṃ, sākhāpalāsaṃ chetvā ādāya "
"pakkanto ‘sāran’ti maññamāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:8.10"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ nānubhavissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:8.11"
msgid "Tathūpamāhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"They’re like the person who mistakes branches and leaves for heartwood, I "
"say."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.201"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:9.1"
msgid ""
"Idha pana, brāhmaṇa, ekacco puggalo saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito "
"hoti:"
msgstr ""
"Next, take a person of good family who has gone forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness …"

msgctxt "mn30:9.2"
msgid ""
"‘otiṇṇomhi jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi "
"upāyāsehi, dukkhotiṇṇo dukkhapareto, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.3"
msgid ""
"appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.4"
msgid "So evaṃ pabbajito samāno lābhasakkārasilokaṃ abhinibbatteti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.5"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attamano hoti na paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.6"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.7"
msgid ""
"Lābhasakkārasilokena ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti "
"asāthaliko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.8"
msgid "So sīlasampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.9"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya attamano hoti, paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.10"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.11"
msgid ""
"‘ahamasmi sīlavā kalyāṇadhammo, ime panaññe bhikkhū dussīlā pāpadhammā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.12"
msgid ""
"Sīlasampadāya ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"sacchikiriyāya na chandaṃ janeti, na vāyamati, olīnavuttiko ca hoti "
"sāthaliko."
msgstr ""
"They become lazy and slack regarding their accomplishment in ethics, not "
"generating enthusiasm or trying to realize those things that are better and "
"finer. …"

msgctxt "mn30:9.13"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi so, brāhmaṇa, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ "
"caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva sāraṃ atikkamma "
"phegguṃ atikkamma tacaṃ, papaṭikaṃ chetvā ādāya pakkanto ‘sāran’ti maññamāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.14"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ, tañcassa atthaṃ nānubhavissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:9.15"
msgid "Tathūpamāhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr "They’re like the person who mistakes shoots for heartwood, I say."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
