msgid "So sīlasampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.9"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya attamano hoti no ca kho paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.10"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.11"
msgid ""
"Sīlasampadāya ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti asāthaliko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.12"
msgid "So samādhisampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.13"
msgid "So tāya samādhisampadāya attamano hoti, paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.14"
msgid "So tāya samādhisampadāya attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.15"
msgid ""
"‘ahamasmi samāhito ekaggacitto, ime panaññe bhikkhū asamāhitā "
"vibbhantacittā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.16"
msgid ""
"Samādhisampadāya ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca, tesaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ sacchikiriyāya na chandaṃ janeti, na vāyamati, olīnavuttiko ca "
"hoti sāthaliko."
msgstr ""
"They become lazy and slack regarding their accomplishment in immersion, not "
"generating enthusiasm or trying to realize those things that are better and "
"finer. …"

msgctxt "mn30:10.17"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi so, brāhmaṇa, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ "
"caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva sāraṃ atikkamma "
"phegguṃ, tacaṃ chetvā ādāya pakkanto ‘sāran’ti maññamāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.18"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ nānubhavissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:10.19"
msgid "Tathūpamāhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr "They’re like the person who mistakes bark for heartwood, I say."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.202"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:11.1"
msgid ""
"Idha pana, brāhmaṇa, ekacco puggalo saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito "
"hoti:"
msgstr ""
"Next, take a person of good family who has gone forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness …"

msgctxt "mn30:11.2"
msgid "‘otiṇṇomhi jātiyā jarāya maraṇena … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.3"
msgid "antakiriyā paññāyethā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.4"
msgid "So evaṃ pabbajito samāno lābhasakkārasilokaṃ abhinibbatteti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.5"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attamano hoti na paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.6"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.7"
msgid ""
"Lābhasakkārasilokena ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti "
"asāthaliko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.8"
msgid "So sīlasampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.9"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya attamano hoti, no ca kho paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.10"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.11"
msgid ""
"Sīlasampadāya ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti asāthaliko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.12"
msgid "So samādhisampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.13"
msgid "So tāya samādhisampadāya attamano hoti, no ca kho paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.14"
msgid "So tāya samādhisampadāya na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.15"
msgid ""
"Samādhisampadāya ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti "
"asāthaliko."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.16"
msgid "So ñāṇadassanaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.17"
msgid "So tena ñāṇadassanena attamano hoti, paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.18"
msgid "So tena ñāṇadassanena attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.19"
msgid ""
"‘ahamasmi jānaṃ passaṃ viharāmi, ime panaññe bhikkhū ajānaṃ apassaṃ "
"viharantī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.20"
msgid ""
"Ñāṇadassanena ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"sacchikiriyāya na chandaṃ janeti, na vāyamati, olīnavuttiko ca hoti "
"sāthaliko."
msgstr ""
"They become lazy and slack regarding their knowledge and vision, not "
"generating enthusiasm or trying to realize those things that are better and "
"finer. …"

msgctxt "mn30:11.21"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi so, brāhmaṇa, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ "
"caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva sāraṃ, phegguṃ "
"chetvā ādāya pakkanto ‘sāran’ti maññamāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.22"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ nānubhavissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn30:11.23"
msgid "Tathūpamāhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr "They’re like the person who mistakes softwood for heartwood, I say."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.203"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:12.1"
msgid ""
"Idha pana, brāhmaṇa, ekacco puggalo saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito "
"hoti:"
msgstr ""
"Next, take a person of good family who has gone forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness, thinking:"

msgctxt "mn30:12.2"
msgid ""
"‘otiṇṇomhi jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi "
"upāyāsehi, dukkhotiṇṇo dukkhapareto, "
msgstr ""
"‘I’m swamped by rebirth, old age, and death; by sorrow, lamentation, pain, "
"sadness, and distress. I’m swamped by suffering, mired in suffering. "

msgctxt "mn30:12.3"
msgid ""
"appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethā’ti."
msgstr "Hopefully I can find an end to this entire mass of suffering.’"

msgctxt "mn30:12.4"
msgid "So evaṃ pabbajito samāno lābhasakkārasilokaṃ abhinibbatteti."
msgstr ""
"When they’ve gone forth they generate possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "mn30:12.5"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attamano hoti, na paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr "They’re not happy with that, and haven’t got all they wished for."

msgctxt "mn30:12.6"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr "They don’t glorify themselves and put others down on account of that."

msgctxt "mn30:12.7"
msgid ""
"Lābhasakkārasilokena ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti "
"asāthaliko."
msgstr ""
"They don’t become lazy and slack regarding their possessions, honor, and "
"popularity, but generate enthusiasm and try to realize those things that are "
"better and finer."

msgctxt "mn30:12.8"
msgid "So sīlasampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr "They become accomplished in ethics."

msgctxt "mn30:12.9"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya attamano hoti, no ca kho paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr "They’re happy with that, but they haven’t got all they wished for."

msgctxt "mn30:12.10"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr "They don’t glorify themselves and put others down on account of that."

msgctxt "mn30:12.11"
msgid ""
"Sīlasampadāya ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti asāthaliko."
msgstr ""
"They don’t become lazy and slack regarding their accomplishment in ethics, "
"but generate enthusiasm and try to realize those things that are better and "
"finer."

msgctxt "mn30:12.12"
msgid "So samādhisampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr "They become accomplished in immersion."

msgctxt "mn30:12.13"
msgid "So tāya samādhisampadāya attamano hoti, no ca kho paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr "They’re happy with that, but they haven’t got all they wished for."

msgctxt "mn30:12.14"
msgid "So tāya samādhisampadāya na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr "They don’t glorify themselves and put others down on account of that."

msgctxt "mn30:12.15"
msgid ""
"Samādhisampadāya ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ "
"dhammānaṃ sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti "
"asāthaliko."
msgstr ""
"They don’t become lazy and slack regarding their accomplishment in "
"immersion, but generate enthusiasm and try to realize those things that are "
"better and finer."

msgctxt "mn30:12.16"
msgid "So ñāṇadassanaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr "They achieve knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "mn30:12.17"
msgid "So tena ñāṇadassanena attamano hoti, no ca kho paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr "They’re happy with that, but they haven’t got all they wished for."

msgctxt "mn30:12.18"
msgid "So tena ñāṇadassanena na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr "They don’t glorify themselves and put others down on account of that."

msgctxt "mn30:12.19"
msgid ""
"Ñāṇadassanena ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"sacchikiriyāya chandaṃ janeti, vāyamati, anolīnavuttiko ca hoti asāthaliko."
msgstr ""
"They don’t become lazy and slack regarding their knowledge and vision, but "
"generate enthusiasm and try to realize those things that are better and "
"finer."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:12.20"
msgid "Katame ca, brāhmaṇa, dhammā ñāṇadassanena uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca?"
msgstr ""
"And what are those things that are better and finer than knowledge and "
"vision?"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:13.1"
msgid ""
"Idha, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi "
"savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"viharati."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant who, quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from "
"unskillful qualities, enters and remains in the first absorption, which has "
"the rapture and bliss born of seclusion, while placing the mind and keeping "
"it connected."

msgctxt "mn30:13.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:14.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ "
"sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ "
"dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, as the placing of the mind and keeping it connected are "
"stilled, a mendicant enters and remains in the second absorption, which has "
"the rapture and bliss born of immersion, with internal clarity and "
"confidence, and unified mind, without placing the mind and keeping it "
"connected."

msgctxt "mn30:14.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This too is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.204"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:15.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca viharati, sato "
"ca sampajāno sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedeti, yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti: ‘"
"upekkhako satimā sukhavihārī’ti tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, with the fading away of rapture, a mendicant enters and remains "
"in the third absorption, where they meditate with equanimity, mindful and "
"aware, personally experiencing the bliss of which the noble ones declare, ‘"
"Equanimous and mindful, one meditates in bliss.’"

msgctxt "mn30:15.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This too is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:16.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā "
"pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ "
"upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, giving up pleasure and pain, and ending former happiness and "
"sadness, a mendicant enters and remains in the fourth absorption, without "
"pleasure or pain, with pure equanimity and mindfulness."

msgctxt "mn30:16.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This too is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:17.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu sabbaso rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā "
"paṭighasaññānaṃ atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṃ amanasikārā ‘ananto ākāso’ti "
"ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant, going totally beyond perceptions of form, with the "
"ending of perceptions of impingement, not focusing on perceptions of "
"diversity, aware that ‘space is infinite’, enters and remains in the "
"dimension of infinite space."

msgctxt "mn30:17.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This too is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:18.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu sabbaso ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma ‘"
"anantaṃ viññāṇan’ti viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant, going totally beyond the dimension of infinite "
"space, aware that ‘consciousness is infinite’, enters and remains in the "
"dimension of infinite consciousness."

msgctxt "mn30:18.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This too is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:19.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu sabbaso viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma ‘"
"natthi kiñcī’ti ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a mendicant, going totally beyond the dimension of infinite "
"consciousness, aware that ‘there is nothing at all’, enters and remains in "
"the dimension of nothingness."

msgctxt "mn30:19.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This too is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:20.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of "
"nothingness, enters and remains in the dimension of neither perception nor "
"non-perception."

msgctxt "mn30:20.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This too is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:21.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā "
"parikkhīṇā honti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of "
"neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation "
"of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, their defilements "
"come to an end."

msgctxt "mn30:21.2"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammo ñāṇadassanena uttaritaro ca paṇītataro ca."
msgstr "This too is something better and finer than knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "mn30:21.3"
msgid "Ime kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammā ñāṇadassanena uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca."
msgstr ""
"These are the things that are better and finer than knowledge and vision."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya22"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:22.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi so, brāhmaṇa, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ "
"caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato sāraṃyeva chetvā ādāya pakkanto "
"‘sāran’ti jānamāno."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a person in need of heartwood. And while wandering in "
"search of heartwood he’d come across a large tree standing with heartwood. "
"He’d cut out just the heartwood and depart knowing it was heartwood."

msgctxt "mn30:22.2"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ anubhavissati."
msgstr "Whatever he needs to make from heartwood, he will succeed."

msgctxt "mn30:22.3"
msgid "Tathūpamāhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr "That’s what this person is like, I say."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya23"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.205"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:23.1"
msgid ""
"Iti kho, brāhmaṇa, nayidaṃ brahmacariyaṃ lābhasakkārasilokānisaṃsaṃ, na "
"sīlasampadānisaṃsaṃ, na samādhisampadānisaṃsaṃ, na ñāṇadassanānisaṃsaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And so, brahmin, this spiritual life is not lived for the sake of "
"possessions, honor, and popularity, or for accomplishment in ethics, or for "
"accomplishment in immersion, or for knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "mn30:23.2"
msgid "Yā ca kho ayaṃ, brāhmaṇa, akuppā cetovimutti—"
msgstr ""
"Rather, the goal, heartwood, and final end of the spiritual life is the "
"unshakable freedom of heart.”"

msgctxt "mn30:23.3"
msgid ""
"etadatthamidaṃ, brāhmaṇa, brahmacariyaṃ, etaṃ sāraṃ etaṃ pariyosānan”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya24"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:24.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, piṅgalakoccho brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin Piṅgalakoccha said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "mn30:24.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "mn30:24.3"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn30:24.4"
msgid "Cūḷasāropamasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "mn30:24.5"
msgid "Opammavaggo niṭṭhito tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "mn30:24.6"
msgid "Moḷiyaphaggunariṭṭhañca nāmo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn30:24.7"
msgid "Andhavane kathipuṇṇaṃ nivāpo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn30:24.8"
msgid "Rāsikaṇerumahāgajanāmo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
#. VAR: Sārūpamo → sārupamo (bj) | sāravaro (si, s1-3) | sāravano (mr)
msgctxt "mn30:24.9"
msgid "Sārūpamo puna piṅgalakoccho."
msgstr ""
